  DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN

    These routines return a string of characters in str, extracted starting at
    the current cursor position in the named window and ending at the right
    margin of the window. Attributes are stripped from the characters. The
    four functions with n as the last argument return a leading substring at
    most n characters long (exclusive of the trailing NUL).

